# @FORMAT COLUMN|SQL_TYPE|NULLABLE|KEY|DESCRIPTION
@D sales|Sales transaction tables
@T STORE_SALES|Store sales facts
SS_SOLD_DATE_SK|INTEGER|Y|FK|Sale date
SS_ITEM_SK|INTEGER|Y|FK|Item sold
SS_QUANTITY|INTEGER|Y||Quantity sold
@R STORE_SALES.SS_SOLD_DATE_SK -> DATE_DIM.D_DATE_SK|fk|Sale date lookup
@R STORE_SALES.SS_ITEM_SK -> ITEM.I_ITEM_SK|fk|Item lookup
